title: A nevv, and merrie prognostication: deuised, after the finest fashion. Made and written for this present yeare, by foure witty doctors as shall appeare, Spendall, Whoball, and Doctor Dews-ace, with them Will Sommer takes his place, they haue consulted all in deede, to solace them, that this shall reede
author: W. W., fl. 1577-1582.
publisher: Printed by Edward All-de, and are to be sold by Iohn Tapp at his shop at Saint Magnus Corner,
